  type:     darcs
  location: http://community.haskell.org/~gwern/archiver/

Library
        exposed-modules:     Network.URL.Archiver
        build-Depends:       base>=4 && < 5, network, HTTP, curl
        ghc-options:         -Wall

Executable archiver
